0.07    2014-05-22
        - Tests will now use local data instead of querying the services.
        - Removed caching functionality; not this module's job.
        - Improved the documentation.

0.06    2013-03-20
        - Now depends on Moose instead of Mouse.
        - Improved the documentation.

0.05    2013-03-19
        - Added support for Reddit.

0.04    2013-03-19
        - Changed default cache expiration to 3 minutes.
        - SHA-encode URLs (for cache keys).
            - Added Digest::SHA 5.84 as requirement.

0.03    2013-03-19
        - Removed unnecessary output to STDERR.

0.02    2013-03-19
        - Added caching of URL requests.

0.01    2013-03-19
        - Initial release.
